benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: PUT /1.0/kb/invoicePayments/{paymentId}/customFields - Modify custom fields to payment

covered: Successful modification of custom fields with required headers (TC01)
Successful modification with all optional headers (TC02)
Successful modification when no custom fields exist initially (TC03)
Successful modification with empty custom fields array (TC04)
Error when paymentId is invalid format (TC05)
Error when paymentId is not found (TC06)

Error when CustomField objects are invalid (TC10)
Unauthorized access attempt (TC11)

gaps: No explicit tests for pagination handling of large datasets.
No tests explicitly cover authorization beyond missing header (e.g., invalid tokens).
No scenarios for rate limiting or throttling.
No tests for caching headers or cache behavior.
Limited validation of concurrent update conflicts or race conditions beyond basic success/error scenarios.
recommendations: Add test scenarios for pagination handling with large datasets.
Include tests for authorization failures such as invalid or expired tokens.
Implement rate limiting/throttling tests to verify system robustness under load.
Add scenarios to verify caching headers like ETag and Cache-Control.
Develop tests for concurrency conflicts and race conditions during updates.
